Exploration and
Mission Operations

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:27.910
Directorate at
NASA headquarters.

00:07:27.910 --> 00:07:29.490
Then we go on to
Bill Farrell who

00:07:29.490 --> 00:07:31.930
is at the Goddard
Space Flight Center.

00:07:31.930 --> 00:07:35.660
This is on the East Coast just
outside of Washington, DC.

